snippet.title: Genshin Impact - The Origins of Amber
snippet.description:
Today's cover's the lore behind Genshin Impact's infamous candle torch lighter: The Knights of Favonius' lone Outrider Amber.

As with all of the character lore vides I've created I really had a lot of fun making it and hope that you all enjoy it.

Join the Teyvat Historia Discord:
https://discord.gg/NBBCaT6tTV
